high_descs: turn around, go to the sink by the window
pick up the tomato from the sink
open the microwave door that is to your left
put the tomato in the microwave, cook it for a few seconds, remove it from the microwave
take the tomato to the fridge that is to the right of the sink
place the tomato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato in the fridge

high_descs: Pick up a tomato to the left of the sink
Heat the tomato in the microwave
Place the tomato inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk over to the counter, after that turn right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Microwave the tomato for a couple seconds then take it out of the microwave and close the door.
Walk over to the white fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated tomato inside on the bottom right shelf, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.
